c: 2
v: 150
t: "Kandi naho uzajya hose (ugashaka gusenga) ujye werekeza uburanga bwawe ku Musigiti Mutagatifu (Al Ka’aba). Naho muzaba muri hose (mugashaka gusenga) mujye muwerekezaho uburanga bwanyu, kugira ngo abantu batazabagiraho urwitwazo, uretse abahuguje (roho zabo) muri bo (bazahora mu mpaka). Bityo ntimuzabatinye ahubwo mujye mutinya njye; kugira ngo mbahundagazeho inema zanjye no kugira ngo muyoboke"